kept.text:
Day 4: Public Equities

Tokenized stocks - listed equities issued natively onchain or represented synthetically. The fastest-growing RWA category in 2026.

Top projects:

@BackedFi - xStocks, the leader in tokenized US equities (Tesla, Nvidia, Alphabet, Apple)

@OndoFinance - Ondo Global Markets, institutional-grade tokenized stock infrastructure

@Securitize - issuer rail for tokenized public equities, backing major institutional launches

@DinariGlobal - dShares, regulated tokenized US stock exposure for non-US investors

@SwarmMarkets - regulated tokenized equities in the EU

@MidasRWA - tokenized US blue-chip equity exposure

$1.21B distributed value (+26.92% / 30d). The fastest-growing RWA category.

Twelve months ago this was a rounding error. Today it's a billion-dollar category compounding at 27% per month.

